Class Git.Commit

  • java.lang.Object
    • Git.Entry
      • Git.Commit
  • Enclosing class:
    Git

    public class Git.Commit
extends Git.Entry
    All the information about the commit:

    what: SHA and pointer to the Tree (contents)
    when: time in msec and as date string
    after: the parents (0, 1, or 2 SHA links)
    who: the author (name and e-mail)
